                                    <tei:note type="layoutNotes">Not all the tiles are engraved. The letters are not production or assembly marks but they were part of a text engraved on the four sides of the impluvium. The beginning of the inscription must have been on the side of the impluvium facing the entrance (see <tei:ref target="http://zotero.org/groups/2552746/items/I6RMMT66"><tei:bibl>La Regina 2021</tei:bibl></tei:ref>: 300).</tei:note>
